Get to know libGDX (https://libgdx.badlogicgames.com/)

Get to know the project source code - see App Description and experiment in a test branch.

Draw various entity textures with gimp or similar - format: 100x100, transparent background.

Create tests that ensure the game's requirements are not violated during execution.

Create a meaningful design for storing levels in binary files (level-data files).
Example binary structure:
    header - magic number - bytes describing enemy data - magic number - bytes describing target data...

Implement a method to read-in level data-files.

Create an interface to efficiently create level-data files.

Design various levels: Specify which entity spawns when and where.
